      • next_chunk_tick

        int next_chunk_tick
        Corruption update speed in game ticks Corruption is updated on separate thread because its calculation takes long and thus its update speed is reduced. To prevent stalling of the main logic loop this calculation is moved to a separate thread so it can calculate within its slower loops free time.
